node.text:
The folks over at @Facebook asked me for the ingredients to my social media special sauce. After much consideration, I declined to be interviewed and left it to the experts.

To my partners in crime @aswissa and @getsuperdigital - we’ve come a long way, bubs 🚀

📺  Tune in for more: Link in bio.

node.text: Mom always said I had a face for radio so voice over seemed like a good fit. This time on #NerfHouse I got to battle my man @guyfieri with the help of @diplo, @skybrown and @klaythompson and they even invited me into their episodes too. If I’m not mistaken they have some premium Nerf content on their instas too. Gonna keep these elite 2.0 blasters handy, always gotta be ready for what’s next with @nerf and this crew… #NerfAd #OnToNerfHouse3?
